{"data":[{"name":"96:1","price":"（預言者*よ、）創造をされた、あなたの主*の御名において（、啓示されたクルアーン*を）読め。","arabic":"ٱقۡرَأۡ بِٱسۡمِ رَبِّكَ ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6107,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"iq'ra bi-is'mi rabbika alladhī khalaqa ","translations":["Read","in (the) name","(of) your Lord","the One Who","created ","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["iq'ra","bi-is'mi","rabbika","alladhī","khalaqa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,830],[2,830,1370],[3,1370,2250],[4,2250,3050],[5,3050,4325]]}},{"name":"96:2","price":"かれは人間を、一塊の凝血からお創りになった。¹","arabic":"خَلَقَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ مِنۡ عَلَقٍ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6108,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　人間の創造の変遷（へんせん）については、巡礼*章５、信仰者たち章１４も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"khalaqa al-insāna min ʿalaqin ","translations":["He created","man","from","a clinging substance","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["khalaqa","al-insāna","min","ʿalaqin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,760],[2,760,2660],[3,2660,3100],[4,3100,4385]]}},{"name":"96:3","price":"（預言者*よ、クルアーン*を）読め。あなたの主*は、最も貴い*お方。","arabic":"ٱقۡرَأۡ وَرَبُّكَ ٱلۡأَكۡرَمُ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6109,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"iq'ra warabbuka al-akramu ","translations":["Read","and your Lord","(is) the Most Generous","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["iq'ra","warabbuka","al-akramu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,880],[2,880,1810],[3,1810,3345]]}},{"name":"96:4","price":"筆（記）を教えて下さったお方。","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي عَلَّمَ بِٱلۡقَلَمِ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6110,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī ʿallama bil-qalami ","translations":["The One Who","taught","by the pen","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","ʿallama","bil-qalami",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,1910],[3,1910,2865]]}},{"name":"96:5","price":"人間に、彼が知らなかったことを教えて下さった（お方）。","arabic":"عَلَّمَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ مَا لَمۡ يَعۡلَمۡ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6111,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿallama al-insāna mā lam yaʿlam ","translations":["Taught","man","what","not","he knew","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿallama","al-insāna","mā","lam","yaʿlam",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,900],[2,900,3010],[3,3010,3350],[4,3350,3770],[5,3770,4615]]}},{"name":"96:6","price":"断じて（、アッラー*の恩恵に対して恩知らずになってはならな）ない！実に人間は、（アッラー*に対して、）まさしく放埓である。","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ لَيَطۡغَىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6112,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā inna al-insāna layaṭghā ","translations":["Nay","Indeed","man","surely transgresses","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","inna","al-insāna","layaṭghā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2380],[2,2380,3430],[3,3430,5480],[4,5480,7055]]}},{"name":"96:7","price":"自らを、十分な者¹と見なすがゆえ。","arabic":"أَن رَّءَاهُ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6113,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　財産、子供、権力において満たされた「十分な者」ということ（アル＝ジャザーイリー５：５９４参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"an raāhu is'taghnā ","translations":["That","he sees himself","self-sufficient","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["an","raāhu","is'taghnā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,300],[2,300,1320],[3,1320,2525]]}},{"name":"96:8","price":"実にあなたの主*にこそ、（来世での）戻り場所があ（り、そこで自分が行ったことを報われることにな）るのである。","arabic":"إِنَّ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ ٱلرُّجۡعَىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6114,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna ilā rabbika al-ruj'ʿā ","translations":["Indeed","to","your Lord","(is) the return","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","ilā","rabbika","al-ruj'ʿā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,1900],[3,1900,2700],[4,2700,3905]]}},{"name":"96:9","price":"言ってみよ、阻む者¹（について）、","arabic":"أَرَءَيۡتَ ٱلَّذِي يَنۡهَىٰ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6115,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　これは不信仰者*の長のアブー・ジャハル*のことだが、彼と同様に善を阻もうとする全ての者も、ここに当てはまる（アッ＝サアディー９３０頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ara-ayta alladhī yanhā ","translations":["Have you seen","the one who","forbids","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["ara-ayta","alladhī","yanhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1070],[2,1070,1980],[3,1980,2915]]}},{"name":"96:10","price":"僕（ムハンマド*）を、彼が礼拝した時に（阻む者について）。","arabic":"عَبۡدًا إِذَا صَلَّىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6116,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿabdan idhā ṣallā ","translations":["A slave","when","he prays","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿabdan","idhā","ṣallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,1500],[3,1500,2545]]}},{"name":"96:11","price":"言ってみよ、もし彼（預言者*）が導きの上にあったとしたら（、いかに彼を礼拝から阻むというのか）？","arabic":"أَرَءَيۡتَ إِن كَانَ عَلَى ٱلۡهُدَىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6117,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ara-ayta in kāna ʿalā al-hudā ","translations":["Have you seen","if","he is","upon","[the] guidance","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["ara-ayta","in","kāna","ʿalā","al-hudā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,990],[2,990,2050],[3,2050,2720],[4,2720,3040],[5,3040,4055]]}},{"name":"96:12","price":"あるいは、（人に）敬虔さ*を命じたのだとしたら（、いかに彼をそこから阻むというのか）？","arabic":"أَوۡ أَمَرَ بِٱلتَّقۡوَىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6118,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"aw amara bil-taqwā ","translations":["Or","he enjoins","[of the] righteousness","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["aw","amara","bil-taqwā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,440],[2,440,1100],[3,1100,2475]]}},{"name":"96:13","price":"言ってみよ、もし彼（阻む者）が、（自分がそこへと招かれているものを）噓呼ばわりし、背を向けたならば、","arabic":"أَرَءَيۡتَ إِن كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6119,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ara-ayta in kadhaba watawallā ","translations":["Have you seen","if","he denies","and turns away","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["ara-ayta","in","kadhaba","watawallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,2090],[3,2090,2930],[4,2930,4195]]}},{"name":"96:14","price":"彼はアッラー*が（、自分のすること全てを）ご覧にな（り、それに対して報われ）るということを、知らなかったのか？","arabic":"أَلَمۡ يَعۡلَم بِأَنَّ ٱللَّهَ يَرَىٰ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6120,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alam yaʿlam bi-anna al-laha yarā ","translations":["Does not","he know","that","Allah","sees","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","yaʿlam","bi-anna","al-laha","yarā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,2160],[3,2160,3620],[4,3620,4440],[5,4440,5545]]}},{"name":"96:15","price":"断じて（、彼の主張は正しく）ない！もしも彼が（預言者*に対する敵対と抑圧を）止めなければ、われら*は必ずや（彼の）前髪を引っ掴んで¹（、業火へ放り込んで）しまおう。","arabic":"كَلَّا لَئِن لَّمۡ يَنتَهِ لَنَسۡفَعَۢا بِٱلنَّاصِيَةِ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6121,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「前髪を掴む」という表現には、その対象への蔑（さげす）み や辱（はずかし）めの意味が含まれている（アル＝クルトゥビー２０：１２５参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā la-in lam yantahi lanasfaʿan bil-nāṣiyati ","translations":["Nay","If","not","he desists","surely We will drag him","by the forelock","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","la-in","lam","yantahi","lanasfaʿan","bil-nāṣiyati",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1020],[2,1020,1940],[3,1940,2460],[4,2460,3940],[5,3940,5350],[6,5350,8675]]}},{"name":"96:16","price":"（言葉は）噓つきで、（行いの）誤った（、彼の）前髪を。","arabic":"نَاصِيَةٖ كَٰذِبَةٍ خَاطِئَةٖ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6122,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"nāṣiyatin kādhibatin khāṭi-atin ","translations":["A forelock","lying","sinful","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["nāṣiyatin","kādhibatin","khāṭi-atin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1960],[2,1960,3170],[3,3170,4615]]}},{"name":"96:17","price":"ならば彼に、自分の会合の場（の仲間たち）を呼ばせて（、援助を乞わせて）みよ。","arabic":"فَلۡيَدۡعُ نَادِيَهُۥ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6123,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"falyadʿu nādiyahu ","translations":["Then let him call","his associates","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["falyadʿu","nādiyahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1090],[2,1090,2505]]}},{"name":"96:18","price":"われら*はザバーニヤ¹を呼んでやるから。","arabic":"سَنَدۡعُ ٱلزَّبَانِيَةَ","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6124,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「ザバーニヤ」とは、「ザブン（押しやる）」という語からの派生語とされ、地獄の住人を押しやる、荒々しく厳しい天使*たち（禁止章６の訳注も参照）のこと（アル＝バガウィー５：２８２参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"sanadʿu al-zabāniyata ","translations":["We will call","the Angels of Hell","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["sanadʿu","al-zabāniyata",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,2875]]}},{"name":"96:19","price":"断じて（、彼の主張は正しく）ない！（使徒*よ、）彼に従わず¹、（あなたの主*に）サジダ*し、お近づきを求めよ。（読誦のサジダ*）","arabic":"كَلَّا لَا تُطِعۡهُ وَٱسۡجُدۡۤ وَٱقۡتَرِب۩","category":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq"],"ayahNumber":6125,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　つまり、崇拝*行為を継続し、沢山行うことから阻（はば）まれて も従うのではない、ということ（イブン・カスィール８：４３９参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā lā tuṭiʿ'hu wa-us'jud wa-iq'tarib ","translations":["Nay","(Do) not","obey him","But prostrate","and draw near (to Allah)","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","lā","tuṭiʿ'hu","wa-us'jud","wa-iq'tarib",""],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,1310],[3,1310,2340],[4,2340,3150],[5,3150,5985]]}}],"chapter":["96 (Al-Alaq)","Al-Alaq","Surah Al-Alaq","Chapter Al-Alaq","Alaq","Surah Alaq","Chapter Alaq","Al Alaq","Surah Al Alaq","Chapter Al Alaq","Surah 96","Chapter 96","The Clot","العلق"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}